    <item>
      <title>力拓与嘉能可的潜在交易或将成为矿业史上最大交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-17/potential-rio-glencore-deal-would-be-mining-s-largest-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，力拓和嘉能可已经讨论过合并两家公司的事宜。如果成功，此次合并将成为有史以来规模最大的矿业交易，并打造出一家可以与长期领头羊必和必拓集团相媲美的巨头。知情人士称，双方的讨论最近在去年年底进行，但目前尚未展开。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-17/potential-rio-glencore-deal-would-be-mining-s-largest-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 09:36:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列与哈马斯达成停火协议后加沙局势如何？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/after-israel-hamas-ceasefire-deal-what-now-for-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过15个月的战争，以色列和哈马斯宣布暂停敌对行动。在最好的情况下，为期六周的停火将无限期延长，这将带来一系列新挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/after-israel-hamas-ceasefire-deal-what-now-for-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 09:25:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员看好英国央行三次降息以提振陷入困境的英国债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pound-falls-as-weak-retail-data-deals-fresh-blow-to-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于零售销售数据弱于预期，支持英国央行采取更积极的宽松政策以提振疲弱的经济增长，英国交易员目前倾向于英国央行今年三次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pound-falls-as-weak-retail-data-deals-fresh-blow-to-confidence</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:45:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
